OL,4,Crush hour police chase
OL,6,FA motorcyclist who reached 130mph
OL,7,Fduring rush hour and failed to stop
OL,8,Ffor police near Swindon has been
OL,9,Fsentenced.
OL,11,FAt around 5.30pm on Friday 12 April,
OL,12,Froads policing officers sighted a
OL,13,Fmotorcycle overtaking on the A4361
OL,14,Ffrom Wroughton in the direction of
OL,15,FBerwick Bassett.
OL,17,FOfficers attempted to catch up with
OL,18,Fthe motorcyclist but he failed to
OL,19,Fstop, performing dangerous overtakes,
OL,20,Fcontravening solid white lines and
OL,21,Ftravelling in excess of 130mph.
