OL,6,FThe pursuit was aborted due to the
OL,7,Fhigh speeds approaching small villages
OL,8,Fand the danger posed to other road
OL,9,Fusers.
OL,11,FHowever, the rider was arrested two
OL,12,Fdays later at his home address.
OL,14,FLawrence Oakford, 33 and of Hamilton
OL,15,FDrive in Market Lavington, pleaded
OL,16,Fguilty to failing to stop for police
OL,17,Fand dangerous driving following the
OL,18,Fpursuit last month, which had to be
OL,19,Fabandoned due to dangerous high speeds.
