OL,6,FHe appeared at Salisbury Magistrates
OL,7,FCourt on 5 May and was sentenced to 24
OL,8,Fweeks imprisonment suspended for 24
OL,9,Fmonths and disqualified from obtaining
OL,10,Fa licence for 24 months.
OL,12,FHe was also ordered to pay #85 Crown
OL,13,FProsecution Costs and a #154 surcharge.
