OL,6,FPC Ben Greening from the Roads
OL,7,FPolicing Unit said: "The speeds at
OL,8,Fwhich Oakford reached whilst failing
OL,9,Fto stop for police were absolutely
OL,10,Funacceptable, especially given this
OL,11,Fwas during a busy time of day and
OL,12,Fapproaching areas where there were
OL,13,Flikely to be pedestrians.
OL,15,F"He showed a total disregard for other
OL,16,Froad users and it is really quite
OL,17,Fextraordinary that nobody was injured
OL,18,For worse killed as a result of his
OL,19,Fstupidity.
